3.replace use roboviz
	a. when use roboviz,maybe can't connect to localhost,it due to hosts file, you also can configure roboviz's config.txt, change localhost to 127.0.0.1
	b. replace cmd rcsoccersim3d ,first find where it is, and edit it with vi or gedit ,chang MON="xxx" xxx is your roboviz.jar path. Also ,you can write like this : 
	cd /usr/local/share/linux-amd64
	MON="./roboviz.sh"		
but it's not stander write


